                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18421212-394-offence-1 t18421212-geo-8"></join>Bermondsey</placeName>, and stealing therein 2 coats, value 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., 1 waistcoat, 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of trowsers, 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 handkerchief, 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 watch, 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; I gown, 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., 1 quilt, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., I bag, 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. 1 half-crown; 5 shillings, his property: and 1 coat, 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 waist<lb></lb>coat, 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of trowsers, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., 1 watch, 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., 1 handkerchief, 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 shirts, 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 2 sovereigns, the property of <persName id="t18421212-name-611" type="victimName">
